desc_long							评测						“The music, the art, the gentle nature – it all creates a completely adorable experience. It’s a real treat.”– Rock, Paper, Shotgun												关于这款游戏							Bob has crashed on a strange planet, lost a bunch of parts for his ship and above all, is late for work!					Find the lost parts and rebuild your ship along the way to solve challenging, physics-based puzzles. You can build your ship any way you like in the ship builder – try to find the coolest ship-design for the puzzle at hand!										Rebuild your ship any way You like					Find the lost parts and tools for Your ship – You’ll need them to solve puzzles!					25 Chapters of solid level design and clever puzzles					Many hours of replayability, with secrets, Achievements, Leaderboards and more											
